actor

Class Hobbit

  • java.lang.Object
    • actor.Actor
      • actor.Hobbit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Hobbit
extends Actor
    The Hobbitis a subclass for Actor super class. The Hobbit creates new characters with derived attributes from the super class. An Additional attribute is added to the subclasses: stealth
    Version:
    Lab Assignment 3: The Hobbit Battlefield Simulator
